summary: Tribal styled, animal themed tattoos and body freckles for modders. For custom races, followers, textures, banners, shields etc.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4][color=#ff0000]Warning!
These are modder resources, not finished mods![/color]

[url=https://flic.kr/p/q6UGmf][img]https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8593/15819426470_4433438fc1_z.jpg[/img][/url][url=https://flic.kr/p/q6UGmf]Sabre cat and deers - Tattoos Testrun 3[/url] by [url=https://www.flickr.com/people/123811473@N05/]LadyFiszi[/url], on Flickr

I wanted to create some standalone Racemenu overlays for body freckles, moles, hair and dirt (mostly for males), and also some animal and mythological creature themed tattoos, but failed every time I tried.

So here are to raw psd files, you can use them for females or males. If you want to create a standalone mod, contact me, and I will be really glad!

[url=https://flic.kr/p/ppFB2X][img]https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8593/15364212293_a64ab452a0_z.jpg[/img][/url][url=https://flic.kr/p/ppFB2X]Tattoo Testrun 2[/url] by [url=https://www.flickr.com/people/123811473@N05/]LadyFiszi[/url], on Flickr
[url=https://flic.kr/p/qospNk][img]https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8663/16006678315_f2fef234aa_z.jpg[/img][/url][url=https://flic.kr/p/qospNk]Rabbits and Turtle - Tattoos Testrun 3[/url] by [url=https://www.flickr.com/people/123811473@N05/]LadyFiszi[/url], on Flickr

Hope you can find good use of them, and don't forget to post screenshots :)

[/size][url=https://flic.kr/p/pps5gA][img]https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8675/15361572344_64d8409f5e_z.jpg[/img][/url][url=https://flic.kr/p/pps5gA]Tattoo Testrun 2[/url] by [url=https://www.flickr.com/people/123811473@N05/]LadyFiszi[/url], on Flickr[/center]
